<html><head><title>Exclusive Omens Alternate Advancement Ability</title></head><body class="newsbody" ><div class=newbody><h2>EQ Vault</h3><h3>Exclusive Omens Alternate Advancement Ability</h3><p>Today we have the first of a new series of new Alternate Advancement Abilities for Omens of War.<br><br>New alternate advancements will be added offering another method of character progression; these alternate advancement will be harder to get than previous releases and offer new and unique skills to master.<br><br>The first ability we have is for the Rogue:<br><i><blockquote>Rogue <br>·       Master of Disguise – This ability allows you to maintain your illusionary disguises across zone boundaries. </blockquote></i><br>I wonder if this could mean more dangerous zone-ins for Omens?  Certainly an interesting ability.  Thanks SOE!</div><p><div classs=copyright><font face=arial size=2 color=#959595>News Story from EQ Vault<br>News Date: Mon 09 Aug 2004<br>Link: http://eqvault.ign.com//index.php#197<br>Printed On: Sun Aug 22 1:55:23 PDT 2004<br>©2004 IGN Entertainment</font></span>